{"tid":1851541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎之決斷！日本首相安倍晉三：「有必要讓台灣加入WHO」","createTime":"2020-01-30T05:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T09:21:24.000Z","uid":186071,"like":767,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"16c03f404e0991ecf6ab1bcec433145064d5aaaf","tid":1851541,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:32:16.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎之決斷！日本首相安倍晉三：「有必要讓台灣加入WHO」<br />\n<br />\n「在瘟疫危機之前，必須放棄政治偏見！」中國爆發的武漢新型冠狀病毒疫情，目前仍處於無法控制的擴散態勢，截至30日上午11點為止，全世界確診感染已達7,816例、至少170人死亡。由於疫情擴散狀態過於猛烈，原本多次否認疫情嚴重性的世界衛生組織（WHO），29日再度改變態度呼籲「全球重視防疫」，並宣布將於30日召開緊急會議、再度決定是否針對中國疫區頒布最高級別警報的「國際公共衛生緊急事件」（PHEIC）&mdash;&mdash;但在WHO會議之前，正在執行武漢撤僑、國內也已出現10起確診病例的日本首相安倍晉三，30日上午卻在參議院質詢中，極為罕見且果斷地表態：東亞防疫缺一不可，「台灣有必要加入WHO！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/global.udn.com/global_vision/amp/story/8662/4311007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fglobal.udn.com%2Fglobal_vision%2Famp%2Fstory%2F8662%2F4311007&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=958f982f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/global.udn.com/global_vision/amp/story/8662/4311007</a>"},{"pid":"f266bbce25c358119b8bd658d15d6b2197a2218c","tid":1851541,"uid":321618,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫護手足 點可以因為一場本可以封關避免嘅病毒而賭上生命<br />\n我地仲未光復到香港啊..<br />\nbtw p牌求推一推... <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥 借刀殺人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850782</a>"},{"pid":"40645506623bc24420242f16cd0bf53c98be55ec","tid":1851541,"uid":249263,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"撐<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求求大家<br />\n明白肺炎好恐怖<br />\n貨源都好緊張<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔好放棄國際戰線<br />\n好多tweets需要人<br />\nhome office 排隊 停課留家 之類<br />\n都拎手機禁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task1 + task2</span></span><br />\n尤其<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">task2</span></span><br />\n全部英美議員講野唔過千<br />\n<br />\n已經連續三日都係咁<br />\n跪求大家唔好放棄國際線<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>Twitter組24小時keep住更新</strong></span><br />\n幫手retweet <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rMemYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=ca4f20b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"f61f82d36482cbea93de32c02c0e27c3be513af4","tid":1851541,"uid":64743,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:33:15.000Z","msg":"一係比台灣入<br />\n一係集體脫離"},{"pid":"50f0dfccb05cf31a616d9984f3a8cc8f755d0ad1","tid":1851541,"uid":77092,"like":202,"dislike":0,"score":202,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:34:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3742f6f76b596063033def2c909cb9c49ea8cd71","tid":1851541,"uid":127929,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f61f82d36482cbea93de32c02c0e27c3be513af4","tid":1851541,"uid":64743,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:33:15.000Z","msg":"一係比台灣入<br />\n一係集體脫離"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-