る」と述べました。<br />\n<br />\nそのうえで、「新型コロナウイルスのこれ以上の感染を防止する観点から、地域が一体となって万全の態勢を可及的速やかに講じる必要がある。政治的な立場において、『この地域は排除する』ということを行っていては、地域全体を含めた健康維持や感染の防止は難しい。引き続き、ＷＨＯでしっかりと主張していきたい」と述べました。</span>"},{"pid":"a0b2e1ecea088d726a20fd7996bdffe9b3d0101b","tid":1851541,"uid":179114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:39:40.000Z","msg":"佢老母果件炸燶既法印係枱底收撚左幾多錢"},{"pid":"d0a11475ecf0d81729959d4e31da09156f82154f","tid":1851541,"uid":335608,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:40:47.000Z","msg":"要另起爐灶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該要整返個Developed Countries Health Organisation 杜絕啲例如世界第二大經濟體暨發展中國家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cba9c2768386b421f5e5258c1f0f9dc872bf1af7","tid":1851541,"uid":284044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:44:37.000Z","msg":"WHO入唔入都把...支持日美歐澳+台灣仔自己開返個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b51577e1ff190b1dda3ac8c378ca2e40c6cc751","tid":1851541,"uid":148980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:45:57.000Z","msg":"要另起爐灶啦, 而家D國際組織比D生蕃玩到爛哂"},{"pid":"ad8026b201d5556567bf8603fa8106ebeb7c5e34","tid":1851541,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:47:31.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"8b49da6e95ab4bd87f34f0ca3822c20aa7858fea","tid":1851541,"uid":224479,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"50f0dfccb05cf31a616d9984f3a8cc8f755d0ad1","tid":1851541,"uid":77092,"like":202,"dislike":0,"score":202,"quote":{"pid":"f61f82d36482cbea93de32c02c0e27c3be513af4","tid":1851541,"uid":64743,"like":116,"dislike":1,"score":115,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:33:15.000Z","msg":"一係比台灣入<br />\n一係集體脫離"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T05:34:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T06:57:07.000Z","msg":"德國肥婆表示不同意 中國已經做得好好